1,325 were some of the most actively traded on the day.\", \"from\": 783, \"to\": 925, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Activity in July puts with strike prices of $1,200  and $1,220 was also almost as busy.\", \"from\": 927, \"to\": 1014, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They all expire on Monday.\", \"from\": 1015, \"to\": 1041, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Combined turnover in the four contracts equated to close to 638,000 ounces of bullion worth more than $800 million.\", \"from\": 1043, \"to\": 1158, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Spot gold prices fell for the third straight session on Wednesday, dropping to a two-week low of $1,261.01 per ounce.\", \"from\": 1160, \"to\": 1277, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Implied volatility typically rises ahead of expiry, but traders said deal-making has been more pronounced than usual, amid heightened risk appetite and nervousness about the result, traders said.\", \"from\": 1279, \"to\": 1474, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are at a line in the sand on which way we are going to go and that's why we are seeing implied volatility in puts and calls spike right now,\\\" said Adam Packard, vice president operations at brokerage Zaner Group in Chicago.\", \"from\": 1476, \"to\": 1703, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tai Wong, director of base and precious metals trading for BMO Capital Markets in New York, said flight to safe haven amid uncertainty over Brexit could push prices to as high as $1,375, the loftiest since March 2014.\", \"from\": 1705, \"to\": 1922, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"An \\\"In\\\" vote is seen as quickly unwinding gold's 5-percent gain in June, as appetite for risk rises and focus returns to the US economy.\", \"from\": 1924, \"to\": 2060, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Prices hit their highest since August 2014 last week as the $5-trillion-a-year gold market rose with other \\\"safe\\\" assets, such as German bunds, the Swiss franc and Japan's yen.\", \"from\": 2062, \"to\": 2238, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Premiums of some out-of-the-money calls were more than two times the cost of out-of-the-money puts, suggesting a more bullish sentiment, said Packard.\", \"from\": 2240, \"to\": 2390, \"entities\": []}]}"